When called interactively, call the function `osm-home'."
  (interactive (list 'home))
  (pcase link
    ('(home)
     (osm-home))
    (`(,lat ,lon ,zoom . ,server)
     (setq server (car server))
     (unless (and server (symbolp server)) (setq server nil)) ;; Ignore comment
